        "category": "other"
      },
      {
        "text": "Bentley Systems iTwin Platform exposed a Cesium ion access token in the source of some web pages. An unauthenticated attacker could use this token to enumerate or delete certain assets.",
        "title": "Risk Evaluation",
        "category": "summary"
      },
      {
        "text": "As of 2026-03-27, the token is no longer present in the web pages and cannot be used to enumerate or delete assets.",
        "title": "Recommended Practices",
        "category": "general"
      },
